Je toto tvoj dom?

201
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:43,790
Prišiel si bez zaklopania.

202
00:18:43,790 --> 00:18:44,700
Zapni si televíziu.

203
00:18:44,700 --> 00:18:45,410
Rýchlo!

204
00:18:47,080 --> 00:18:49,330
Poznáte slovo,
 "anti-fanúšik"?

205
00:18:49,580 --> 00:18:52,580
Kórejská popová star,
 Hou Zhun a jeho anti-fanúšik

206
00:18:52,580 --> 00:18:53,950
