270
00:22:18,500 --> 00:22:20,790
To teda nie.

271
00:22:21,450 --> 00:22:22,250
Manažér Wang.

272
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:27,830
Tá vec s tvojou antifanúšičkou....

273
00:22:28,450 --> 00:22:29,450
Mali by sme sa chytiť šance

274
00:22:29,870 --> 00:22:32,450
a ukázať voči nej toleranciu,

275
00:22:32,870 --> 00:22:35,910
aby si si zlepšil svoj imidž.

276
00:22:35,910 --> 00:22:39,870
Budeš centrom pozornosti.

277
00:22:41,410 --> 00:22:44,080
Počkajte slečna Fang.

278
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,250
Prosím.

279
00:22:46,250 --> 00:22:48,040
Prosím,
vypočujte si ma.

280
00:22:48,040 --> 00:22:49,910
Dáva vám to zmysel?

281
00:22:49,910 --> 00:22:52,410
Viete čo mi Hou Zhun urobil?

282
00:22:52,410 --> 00:22:55,000
Vyhodil ma a jeho
fanúšikovia ma zmlátili.

283
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:55,910
Stratila som prácu

284
00:22:55,910 --> 00:22:57,290
a moju spolubývajúcu.

285
00:22:57,290 --> 00:22:59,660
Stane sa zo mňa bezdomovkyňa.

286
00:22:59,660 --> 00:23:00,750
Potešilo vás to?

287
00:23:00,750 --> 00:23:01,500
Je naozaj trápne žiť takto

288
00:23:01,750 --> 00:23:03,500
